tafsir[17]{c,v,t}:
  86,1,"Alla woondirii kammu e hoodere fuɗoore jemma."
  86,2,"Hol ko anndin Ma -aan nelaado- ko woni fiyaaku hoodere mawnde nde?"
  86,3,"Konde hoodere yuliroore kammu njalbeeri mayre."
  86,4,"Alah fittaandu si wonah Alla na wakkili e mayru malayka ndeenoowo golle mayru ngam hasboore ñande darnga."
  86,5,"Yo aade ndaartina ko e hoɗum Alla tagri mbo, haa laaɓana mbo kattane Alla e ronkere aade."
  86,6,"Alla tagirii mbo e ndiyam njuppoto ɗam e rannga."
  86,7,"ɗam ndiyam na yalta hakkunde noorol keeci gorko e ƴi*e ɓernde debbo."
  86,8,"Alla ceniiɗo o -nde O tagi mbo e ndiyam koyɗam-na hattani ummindede mbo caggal maayde ngam hasboore e njoɓdi."
  86,9,"ñande cuuɗiiɗi kuncaa, ko wonno e ɓerɗe e anniyaaji e piɓle njaltina, ko laba seera ko boni."
  86,10,"Woodanaani aade e oon ñalawma cemmbe duñooje lepte Alla wonah balloowo."
  86,11,"Alla woondirii kammu ngu toɓo, sabu hongo tellaro toon laawol caggal laawol."
  86,12,"Alla woondirii leydi ndi petti ɗi puɗi e ɓeynaaɗe e leɗɗe njaltata."
  86,13,"Pellet o Quraana telliiɗo e muhamadu komb konngol ceerndawol hakkunde goonga e meere e hakkunde goongo e fenaande."
  86,14,"Mbo wonah fijirde e meere, kammbo ko mbo soobe e goongo."
  86,15,"Pellet fennuɓe ɓe hoɓe pewja peeje keewɗe ngam ɓe ndutta noddaandu makko ndu, ɓe mbonna ndu."
  86,16,"Miin mi fewja feere sabu ɓannginde diine e ittude meere."
  86,17,"Muñan -aan nelaaɗo- ɓee heefereeɓe muñagol setta, wota heñana leptugol ɓe e halkude ɓe."
